{
  "chapter": 22,
  "chapter_summary": "项少龙回到雅夫人别宫，收到郭纵打造的千枝飞针等物。公子盘前来拜访，对项少龙崇拜有加，透露少君表面口硬心中佩服。项少龙教导公子盘墨子剑法，又在浴池中向雅夫人询问六国形势，雅夫人分析齐燕距秦远无切肤之痛，各国只顾扩张领土，项少龙断言六国必被秦灭。次日公子盘恳求项少龙娶其母赵妮，项少龙答应考虑。赵妮出现致谢，项少龙趁机邀她到林中亭幽会，突破她九年守节的心理防线，两人在亭中亲吻缠绵。侍女盈儿来报陶方求见，赵妮逃走。陶方密告送赵倩赴魏大梁之路危机四伏，马贼土霸和齐国均欲破坏联姻，内鬼疑为赵穆或少原君。项少龙再访赵妮书斋，两人终于共赴云雨。公子盘归来察觉母亲变化，项少龙决心保护心爱女子，重燃斗志。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "可是很快又被他们打倒了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 9
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父真了不起，把那群力士打得东倒西歪，少君虽然口硬，但我看他心中是挺服气的。没试过你厉害之处的人，自告奋勇要来找你，全给少君拒绝了。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "什么？你们这群横行霸道的小恶人，终于遇上克星了吗？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "雅姨不也是给师父收拾了吗？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌姊姊真美，宫内无人可及。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "小子！告诉我，你和女人来过了没有？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然来过，不过比起师父就差得远了，连雅姨都给你降伏，我们早封你作赵国对女人最有吸引力的男人。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你碰过娘没有？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我刚问过娘，她脸都红透，将我赶了出来，但我却看出她心中喜欢你呢！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "为何各国明知秦人的厉害，仍不能团结起来？像我们今天到魏国去，明是修好，其实是不安好心？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你若再不停止摸人，教人家怎能好好答你？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "说吧！",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "少龙！芳儿都想听啊！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "text": "这样可以了吧！",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_ting_fang",
      "speaker_name": "乌廷芳",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "雅姊快说。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "雅夫人",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "最主要的原因，我想是地理上的问题，例如齐、燕两国，距秦颇远，根本不像我们般受到切肤之痛。谁也知道若想强大，就要扩张领土，所以燕人见我们长平一役元气大伤，趁机来侵，哪有空闲去想团结抗秦。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 75
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ya_fu_ren",
      "text": "雅儿的分析很有道理，我肯定六国迟早会给强秦灭掉，我们应早作打算。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父！你娶我娘好吗？宫内外想侵占她的人很多，若她给我憎厌的人得到了，我情愿自尽。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 109
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "想不到原来你这么疼你的娘，可是尽管我有娶你娘的心，还须大王恩准，现在我一无军功，二来职位低微，怎能得大王首肯，所以这事迟点再谈吧！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "那娘怎办才好，我从未见过她用那种看你的眼神望过别的男人。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 117
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生早安，大恩大德，不敢言谢，惟有来世结草衔环以报。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "娘啊！何用来世呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "小盘你口不择言，对先生和娘均无礼至极，你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "小盘还不快溜？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 130,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "我们到那林中亭坐一会儿好吗？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 145
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "项先生……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生尊重赵妮的名节好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 159
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "我项少龙怎会强人所难，来！我们到亭内坐一会儿，共享桂花幽香。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你要先答应人家守礼才行。",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "夫人请入亭小坐。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "嗅到桂花香吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "桂花怎及夫人香呢？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 195
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不是说好不会对妾身无礼吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "怎么才算无礼，还是周公大礼呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 201
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "求求你，截着她，不要被她看到人家这样子。",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bing_nv_ying_er",
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_nv_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "盈儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "乌府的陶公来找先生，雅夫人的小昭姊姊陪他来的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_bing_nv_ying_er",
      "text": "姊姊请着他等一会儿，我立即便到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bing_nv_ying_er",
      "speaker_name": "盈儿",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生叫我盈儿吧！",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我们刚接到秘密消息，今天你送三公主赵倩到魏国的首都大梁，并非无惊无险，不但马贼土霸摩拳擦掌，听说齐国亦想破坏魏、赵这宗婚姻交易，要找人坏赵倩的贞操，少龙务要非常小心。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "这事应属极端秘密，为何消息竟会泄露出来呢？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "当然是有人故意放消息出来，照我看，这内鬼不出赵穆或少原君两个奸徒的其中之一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_tao_fang",
      "text": "这对他们有什么好处？少原君和我乘同一条船，若遭攻击，他恐亦不能身免吧！",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tao_fang",
      "speaker_name": "陶方",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "内情可能非常复杂，我来是特别提醒你，明天清早你们便要起程了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "夫人还在恼我无礼吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你早已无礼了，妾身还有什么好怪先生的呢？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "夫人恩宠，我项少龙受宠若惊哩！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "先生明天要出使到魏国。唉！你教妾身怎样度过这段时光？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ni",
      "text": "光阴苦短，夫人是否怪我急色？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我又打垮两个人，他们都说要拜你做师父。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "speaker_name": "公子盘",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "师父和娘……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ni",
      "speaker_name": "赵妮",
      "listener": "char_gong_zi_pan",
      "text": "不准小盘再说。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 22,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    }
  ],
